{"tid":938242,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找錶鄉的故事 非曬命 有圖","createTime":"2018-12-12T07:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T10:30:01.000Z","uid":11030,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"916a212726e3fd30ed523aa9ae7a3b97727344ef","tid":938242,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"如題 近日睇到篇有關錶既文章 突然心血來潮想追查隻錶既來歷 但係奈隻錶logo都冇 <br />\n所以想睇下各位絲巴打金精火眼睇得出依隻錶係咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資料：<br />\n日本 神戶購物街店買<br />\n應該係石英錶<br />\n初步估計可能係d業餘工藝師既手作<br />\n可能係cheap野 所以應該追尋到既機會好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg&h=143c908a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg&h=28ad8fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg&h=ad09a2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n非曬命 純心血來潮 想知道佢既來歷<br />\n感激各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bd6621da39191d2cb1a34149f0ff26241b9f5c","tid":938242,"uid":29784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"